{"tid":188843,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想幫主人轉狗糧，求解答","createTime":"2017-04-06T03:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T02:13:32.000Z","uid":10218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c425d8e789dad5e50f9143c3de1d9990fda4e5","tid":188843,"uid":10218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:59:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的，最近想幫主子轉過隻狗糧<br />\n本身食開Hills羊肉+飯，但見佢勁飲水，<br />\n上網睇同聽呢到巴打講先知好多味精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當初都係獸醫介紹 （我知錯我後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n所以想幫主子轉過隻<br />\n<br />\n睇完覺得Canidae 同 oven baked都幾好 無論價錢 成份（都係揀返羊肉）都符合budget同心水<br />\n<br />\n但有人話oven baked啲便便會好臭<br />\nCanidae又無咩特別 淨係話平靚正<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位巴絲 邊隻好啲呢？<br />\n麻煩幫幫小弟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢兩隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/06/115756_fb93b337a5b8e98e9424e5bfa8e122ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F06%2F115756_fb93b337a5b8e98e9424e5bfa8e122ab.jpg&h=1ae4e63b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/06/115800_4a3c87fd5bb23a745dccf2504272e23b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F06%2F115800_4a3c87fd5bb23a745dccf2504272e23b.jpg&h=ee6e1d1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac005582c7ae20c933cbf73d3409699d800269c6","tid":188843,"uid":15812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:02:22.000Z","msg":"自己買雞/牛煮都可以 用水滾熟佢就得 可以加幾條菜"},{"pid":"20ad8c4549a62b7d091ef1a3fa87b3b6291e7914","tid":188843,"uid":10218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T17:35:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己買雞/牛煮都可以 用水滾熟佢就得 可以加幾條菜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我要返工煮唔到 平日由屋企人代餵<br />\n要簡單方便為主 所以只可以食狗糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯有weekend得閒就煮下"},{"pid":"a006f8840f2e815565d3b52f540033e20a69842f","tid":188843,"uid":10218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T17:38:32.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲可以解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出賣主子拋磚引玉 大家幫下佢啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WT4286j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWT4286j.jpg&h=de46b023&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63d95934a92943ab29d0a6ed2874d4ecf33b5f70","tid":188843,"uid":10616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T19:38:29.000Z","msg":"Almo Nature垃撚垃，唔好買"},{"pid":"c578b0e7805a654f72b9f64a4b0ce0ca967acf19","tid":188843,"uid":81906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:12:31.000Z","msg":"主人好cute啊~<br />\n我主人食開Canidae grain free,唔錯,屎靚"},{"pid":"0cf852a9704abfb7ad01291d9e8968d6200b2687","tid":188843,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:11:01.000Z","msg":"我隻狗食開Fromm<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/07/091021_32d2734bcce36322d915e461b6ef7358.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F07%2F091021_32d2734bcce36322d915e461b6ef7358.jpg&h=25c25a06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網都見到有人讚呢隻糧<br />\n我有個網買糧 買用品都算平<br />\n而且牌子齊全耶"},{"pid":"60c1fa1197a77e62b517ac7512beed9bfa0340b8","tid":188843,"uid":10218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:25:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻狗食開Fromm<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/